data.description: Check out this beautiful fully renovated manufactured home nestled on 3.384 acres. The property features barbed wire fencing, metal barn with pens and storage area making the perfect place for all your AG projects, and barbed wire fencing around the property as a whole. The home feature all new bathrooms, new updated kitchen with custom cabinets and butcher block counter tops, split floor plan with a true master suite and walk in closet, custom sliding barn doors, and a freshly updated exterior with all new paint and trim! Current owners had the acreage professionally cleared to be ready for all your country dreams. Call Dustanna with Hunter Ranch and Realty at 325-864-0409 for more information.
